against Dagada and other officials implicated, and they will face disciplinary
enquiries for their roles in the breaches of legislation and governance
procedures.Dagada has been replaced with
Funzela Ngobeni, who was the MMC of Development planning.Mashaba condemned the allegations
against Dagada.“As an Executive Mayor, I cannot
necessarily detect the willingness of people to engage in regrettable actions.
However, we can and will continue to ensure that no act against the residents
of our City goes unpunished, especially in those we trust to deliver change,”
he said.